                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>No official record of this conversation has been found. According to the very
                    brief mention in Alanbrooke, pp. 507–508, Smith anticipated that a solution to
                    the problems regarding future strategy would be put forward which would limit
                    operations in the European area for the benefit of the Pacific theater.</p>
            </div>
